  "description": {
    "zh": "老兄，快进来，有事儿找你。听好了。我发现了可疑的事情。那些外来的人经常在晚上和一些本地人做一些见不得人的事情。我试着调查过，说不定还能分一杯羹，但是事情黄了。他们不带我一起，真是混蛋。帮我个忙，给这些家伙上一课，让他们知道谁才是这里真正的大人物。",
    "en": "All right, mate, come in quick, got work to do. So listen up. Something really fishy's going on. Those big shots and foreign thugs are doing some kind of murky shit at night with some of the locals. I tried to investigate and maybe get my cut, but got fucked over. They didn't cut me in, those muts. Help a brother out, teach those bastards a lesson, show them who's the real deal in this town, so that it doesn't happen again."
  },
